13:21.935 --> 13:24.271
- HE WAS ABOUT 30,
TALLISH,

13:24.271 --> 13:28.241
LONG HAIR, LONG BEARD,
SMALL DICK...

13:28.241 --> 13:30.277
YOU KNOW, 'CAUSE GUYS
WITH BIG ONES

13:30.277 --> 13:32.179
