CAN SHOCK YOU ANYMORE.

14:17.023 --> 14:18.425
AND THEN--

14:18.425 --> 14:20.393
WHAT IS IT WITH MEN
AND THEIR JOHNSONS--

14:20.393 --> 14:22.062
SHAKING THEM ON BUSES,

14:22.062 --> 14:25.799
