IF THERE WAS MORE BROCCOLI.

15:06.740 --> 15:09.242
AND YOU NEVER KNOW
WHAT'S GONNA SET HER OFF.

15:09.242 --> 15:10.944
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
PUT THAT BACK ON.

15:10.944 --> 15:13.146
- I'M CHANGING.
[cell phone rings]

15:13.146 --> 15:14.948
- TERESA WILL BE HERE
AT 2:00.

15:14.948 --> 15:16.516
- WHO'S THAT?
- NOTARY PUBLIC,

15:16.516 --> 15:18.285
