15:25.025 --> 15:26.459
PUT YOUR SHIRT ON!

15:26.459 --> 15:28.028
- HEY, I'M CHANGING.

15:28.028 --> 15:30.096
I'M GONNA GO TAKE A LOOK
AT YOUR CAR.

15:30.096 --> 15:32.432
- OKAY.
- ON THAT FOOT?

15:32.432 --> 15:33.833
- I CAN HANDLE IT.

15:33.833 --> 15:35.268
- IF YOU CAN HANDLE IT,
MAYBE YOU CAN HANDLE

15:35.268 --> 15:37.070
