SEE IF THERE'S

16:05.165 --> 16:08.668
SOME MORE BROCCOLI.

16:08.668 --> 16:11.037
- FINE. COME ON.

16:11.037 --> 16:14.040
TERESA, HERE, 2:00.

16:18.044 --> 16:19.546
- HOLY SHIT.

16:19.546 --> 16:20.914
- A LOT OF RED DOTS.

16:20.914 --> 16:22.649
- ALL THOSE RED DOTS
ARE SEX OFFENDERS

16:22.649 --> 16:23.983
