16:23.983 --> 16:25.218
- ALL RIGHT,
CHECK THIS OUT.

16:25.218 --> 16:27.153
CHILD RAPIST
THREE BLOCKS OVER,

16:27.153 --> 16:29.222
DID FIVE YEARS
AND OUT ON PROBATION.

16:29.222 --> 16:31.691
- HOW DOES A CHILD RAPIST
ONLY GET FIVE YEARS?

16:31.691 --> 16:33.360
- HE DOESN'T--
HE GETS FIVE YEARS,

16:33.360 --> 16:34.928
PLUS THE BEATING OF THIS LIFE.
LET'S GO.

16:34.928 --> 16:36.262
- I THOUGHT
WE WERE GONNA FIX THE POOL.

16:36.262 --> 16:37.530
- NO, NO, NO,
YOU SHOULD COME, CARL.

16:37.530 --> 16:38.832
GRAB THE BAT.
- AWESOME.

16:38.832 --> 16:40.200
- HEY, YOU WANT HELP?

16:40.200 --> 16:41.935
MY DAD ALWAYS LOVES
A GOOD PERV POSSE.

16:41.935 --> 16:43.703
- SO WE'RE JUST FORGETTING
ABOUT THE GUY ON THE BUS?

16:43.703 --> 16:45.905
- HELL, NO, I'M GONNA
TEACH YOU SELF-DEFENSE--

16:45.905 --> 16:47.974
MILKOVICH STYLE.
COME ON.

16:47.974 --> 16:50.310
- ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO.

16:50.310 --> 16:51.911
YO, WE'RE GOING
TO JUMP A PEDOPHILE.

16:51.911 --> 16:53.646
YOU WANT TO COME?
- AW, SOUNDS GREAT.

16:53.646 --> 16:55.915
BUT I CAN'T.

16:57.417 --> 16:58.718
- YOU'RE ACTING CAGEY, OKAY?

16:58.718 --> 17:01.287
AND THERE'S BEEN
AN ESCALADE PARKED

17:01.287 --> 17:02.856
ACROSS THE STREET
FOR LONGER THAN MAKES SENSE.

17:02.856 --> 17:05.325
WHAT'S GOING ON?

17:05.325 --> 17:08.361
I DON'T WANT TO KNOW?

17:08.361 --> 17:11.765
'CAUSE IF YOU TOLD ME,
I'D HAVE TO TELL FIONA,

17:11.765 --> 17:13.867
WHICH WOULD UPSET
THE DELICATE PEACE

17:13.867 --> 17:17.404
WE'VE RECENTLY ESTABLISHED?

17:17.404 --> 17:18.772
RIGHT.

17:18.772 --> 17:20.940
- HAVE FUN
WAILING ON THE PEDOPHILE.

17:20.940 --> 17:22.542
- IS THERE ANY WAY NOT TO?

17:22.542 --> 17:24.210
- THANK YOU.

17:24.210 --> 17:26.146
- NO, THANK YOU, MARTA.
THANK YOU.

17:26.146 --> 17:29.382
- NOW YOU STAY STRONG.
- COME ON, BABY.

17:29.382 --> 17:32.051
- HELLO.
MAY I HELP YOU?

17:32.051 --> 17:34.254
- I HOPE SO.
I'M FRANK GALLAGHER.

17:34.254 --> 17:36.222
MAY I START BY SAYING
THANK YOU

17:36.222 --> 17:38.458
FOR ALL YOU DO
FOR OUR SUFFERING LITTLE ONES.

17:38.458 --> 17:41.628
- THANK YOU, MR. GALLAGHER.

17:41.628 --> 17:44.230
- THIS IS MY SON HYMIE.

17:44.230 --> 17:47.400
HE WAS BORN
WITH AN EXTRA CHROMOSOME,

17:47.400 --> 17:50.103
THROUGH NO FAULT OF HIS OWN--
DOWN SYNDROME.

17:50.103 --> 17:52.872
IT'S A LIFELONG CONDITION.
IT'S IRREVERSIBLE.

17:52.872 --> 17:54.340
- HE'S A BEAUTIFUL BOY.

17:54.340 --> 17:56.209
AREN'T YOU, HYMIE?
YES, YOU ARE.

17:56.209 --> 17:59.446
- AND BELIEVE IT OR NOT,
HE IS ALREADY,

17:59.446 --> 18:02.649
AT SUCH A YOUNG AGE,
AN AVID SPORTS FAN.

18:02.649 --> 18:04.050
- IS THAT SO?

18:04.050 --> 18:06.453
- HE CAN WATCH
A BALL DRIBBLE

18:06.453 --> 18:08.555
UP AND DOWN A COURT
FOR HOURS,

18:08.555 --> 18:10.056
ENDLESSLY FASCINATED.

18:10.056 --> 18:13.059
HIS LITTLE FACE
JUST LIGHTS UP WITH JOY.

18:13.059 --> 18:15.128
IT WOULD BE SO WONDERFUL

18:15.128 --> 18:19.799
IF HE COULD SEE IT
ALL HAPPEN IN REAL LIFE.

18:19.799 --> 18:21.801
- I'M SORRY, MR. GALLAGHER.

18:21.801 --> 18:24.037
I-I THINK
YOU MAY BE CONFUSED.

18:24.037 --> 18:28.675
OUR ORGANIZATION
WORKS WITH DYING CHILDREN,

18:28.675 --> 18:31.277
NOT CHILDREN WITH DOWN'S.

18:31.277 --> 18:34.280
- OF COURSE.

18:34.280 --> 18:36.950
OF COURSE.
I KNOW THAT.

18:36.950 --> 18:39.118
[crying]

18:39.118 --> 18:42.288
