THAT'S DYING.

18:42.288 --> 18:44.524
[sobs]
- OH, I'M SORRY.

18:44.524 --> 18:46.125
- THANK YOU.

18:46.125 --> 18:48.862
[blows nose, sobs]

19:00.340 --> 19:02.675
- DRIVE.

19:06.312 --> 19:09.649
- [chuckles]

19:09.649 --> 19:12.352
