19:43.283 --> 19:45.251
- OH, SHIT.

19:45.251 --> 19:49.088
YOU'RE THE EIGHTH-GRADE TEACHER
WHO SCREWED HER STUDENT, RIGHT?

19:49.088 --> 19:51.224
YOU WERE ON TV.

19:51.224 --> 19:54.527
