A MISTAKE.

20:00.300 --> 20:02.869
[sighs] I'M SURE
THERE ARE REAL CRIMINALS

20:02.869 --> 20:04.571
IN THE THE NEIGHBORHOOD
THAT YOU CAN BEAT UP

20:04.571 --> 20:06.072
