20:23.256 --> 20:25.525
- UH, NO,
BUT SHE FUCKS LITTLE KIDS.

20:25.525 --> 20:27.660
- IT WAS ONE KID,
AND HE WASN'T THAT LITTLE.

20:27.660 --> 20:29.862
- LOOK, HE WAS 14.
SHE WAS HIS TEACHER.

20:29.862 --> 20:32.198
DO WE REALLY WANT A PEDOPHILE
LIVING IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD?

20:32.198 --> 20:33.833
- SHIT, IF IT WAS 14
AND HAD A TEACHER

20:33.833 --> 20:35.935
WHO LOOKED LIKE THAT
AND WANTED IT?

20:35.935 --> 20:38.638
MAN, I'M GETTING WOOD
JUST THINKING ABOUT THAT.

20:38.638 --> 20:41.207
YO, ANGIE?

20:41.207 --> 20:42.809
- YEAH?

20:42.809 --> 20:44.844
- YOU WANT TO FUCK?

20:44.844 --> 20:46.846
- SURE.

20:51.417 --> 20:53.086
- NOW, SEE, I THOUGHT
YOU TWO WERE, UH...

20:53.086 --> 20:54.487
- SHUT UP.

20:54.487 --> 20:56.589
