THE COPS 100 TIMES.

21:05.098 --> 21:06.799
SHOULD'VE--
CREEPY FUCKING ARAB DUDE

21:06.799 --> 21:08.501
FUCKING MY LITTLE BROTHER.
- I WAS 15.

21:08.501 --> 21:10.370
I WAS OLD ENOUGH
TO MAKE MY OWN DECISIONS.

21:10.370 --> 21:12.071
- YOU WERE A KID.
HE WAS A MAN.

21:12.071 --> 21:13.840
- SAYS YOU.

21:13.840 --> 21:15.541
- YOU REALLY WANT THIS CHICK
LIVING IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD?

21:15.541 --> 21:16.976
