AND A 30-YEAR-OLD DUDE?

21:20.880 --> 21:23.182
- UGH, IT'S DIFFERENT.
- BULLSHIT IT'S DIFFERENT.

21:23.182 --> 21:26.019
- LOOK, SHE'S NOT HANGING AROUND
THE PARK WITH LOLLIPOPS.

21:26.019 --> 21:27.353
SHE FELL IN LOVE.

21:27.353 --> 21:28.755
- IT'S GOT NOTHING TO DO
WITH LOVE.

21:28.755 --> 21:31.557
THIS CHICK
IS A STANDARD-ISSUE PEDOPHILE,

21:31.557 --> 21:34.360
AND I'M GONNA PROVE IT.

21:37.997 --> 21:42.735
- [shouting in Portuguese]

21:42.735 --> 21:46.239
- SORRY I'M LATE.
- I HATE THIS I.N.S. BULLSHIT.

21:46.239 --> 21:49.709
