- 2:00.

22:09.696 --> 22:11.264
- I GOT IT.

22:13.733 --> 22:15.835
- SHE HATES ME, DOESN'T SHE?

22:15.835 --> 22:17.804
- NO. SHE JUST
DON'T KNOW YOU YET.

22:17.804 --> 22:20.640
- I MEAN, I GET IT--I WOULD HATE
ME, TOO, IF I WERE HER.

22:20.640 --> 22:22.742
