KNOW IF KYLE'S YOURS.

22:32.952 --> 22:35.221
I WAS REALLY GETTING AROUND
BACK THEN.

22:35.221 --> 22:37.890
SO V HAS NOTHING
TO WORRY ABOUT.

22:40.493 --> 22:42.495
WHAT?
WHAT'D I SAY?

22:42.495 --> 22:44.564
- YOU THINK KYLE
COULD BE MINE?

22:44.564 --> 22:46.399
- YOU DIDN'T DO THAT MATH?

22:46.399 --> 22:50.103
SHIT. SORRY.

22:50.103 --> 22:52.972
- CANCER?

22:52.972 --> 22:55.108
HOW DID I GET CANCER?

22:55.108 --> 22:57.510
- YOU MUST HAVE CAUGHT IT
FROM GRAMMY, SON.

22:57.510 --> 22:59.979
IF SHE HAD KNOWN THAT SHE HAD
THE CONTAGIOUS KIND,

22:59.979 --> 23:01.681
