SO MUCH TIME

23:01.681 --> 23:03.549
WITH YOU IN THE BASEMENT,
COOKING METH.

23:03.549 --> 23:06.452
- AM I GOING TO DIE?

23:07.820 --> 23:09.555
- I HOPE NOT.

23:09.555 --> 23:12.258
BUT RIGHT NOW
WE HAVE TO FIGHT

23:12.258 --> 23:15.294
AND FIGHT HARD.

23:15.294 --> 23:18.498
