WITH ME, CARL?

23:21.300 --> 23:22.635
[razor whirring]

23:22.635 --> 23:24.871
- WHY DO WE HAVE
TO SHAVE IT?

23:24.871 --> 23:27.306
- DIDN'T YOU EVER SEE ANY SHOWS
ABOUT CANCER?

23:27.306 --> 23:30.209
CANCER PEOPLE ARE ALWAYS BALD.

23:30.209 --> 23:31.811
- GRAMMY WASN'T BALD.

23:31.811 --> 23:33.613
- GRAMMY HATED LIFE.

23:33.613 --> 23:36.649
SHE WANTED TO DIE,
BUT YOU LOVE LIFE.

23:36.649 --> 23:38.484
AND ONE
OF THE MOST IMPORTANT WAYS

23:38.484 --> 23:40.319
YOU CAN FIGHT THE CANCER

23:40.319 --> 23:45.158
IS TO LET THE SUNRAYS
IN THROUGH YOUR SKULL.

23:45.158 --> 23:47.794
- WHY ARE YOU SHAVING
CARL'S HEAD?

23:47.794 --> 23:49.562
- LICE.

23:49.562 --> 23:51.164
- SINCE WHEN DO YOU...

23:51.164 --> 23:52.698
PARENT?

23:52.698 --> 23:54.901
- SINCE YOU DROPPED THE BALL.

23:54.901 --> 23:58.704
