JUMPING OFF HIS SCALP.

23:58.704 --> 24:00.840
- WELL, MAKE SURE
YOU WASH THE SHEETS TOO, OKAY?

24:00.840 --> 24:03.876
- I LOOK LIKE A WOMAN?

