- MM-HMM.
- OKAY, BREATHE DEEPER.

37:54.973 --> 37:56.475
- MM.
- SLOWLY.

37:56.475 --> 37:58.710
- MM. MM-HMM.
- SLOWLY.

37:58.710 --> 38:00.479
SLOW.

38:00.479 --> 38:02.681
OKAY?

38:02.681 --> 38:06.418
- OKAY.
- GOOD.

38:06.418 --> 38:08.453
- WHAT'S, UH--
WHAT--WHAT'S THAT?

38:08.453 --> 38:10.155
THAT'S, UM--
AH, THAT'S WEIRD.

38:10.155 --> 38:12.124
- [giggles]
- YEAH, THAT'S--

38:12.124 --> 38:14.126
THAT'S COLD.
WHAT--WHAT IS THAT?

38:14.126 --> 38:15.627
- WELL, YOU TRIMMED
MY HEDGES,

38:15.627 --> 38:18.163
AND NOW I AM TRIMMING YOURS.

38:18.163 --> 38:20.799
- WAIT, WHAT--
WHAT IS THAT, FUCKING NAIR?

38:20.799 --> 38:22.300
- YOU'RE FRESH AND CLEAN NOW,

38:22.300 --> 38:26.071
JUST LIKE A BABY, PHILLIP.
- WAIT, NO, WHAT--

38:26.071 --> 38:28.340
OH, SHIT.

38:28.340 --> 38:30.642
- YOU SAID YOU CATERED
TO DYING CHILDREN.

38:30.642 --> 38:34.179
- SIR, THE BULLS ONLY GIVE US
SO MANY PACKAGES PER SEASON

38:34.179 --> 38:35.480
AND IT TAKES MONTHS.
- OW!

38:35.480 --> 38:37.182
WHAT THE FUCK, FRANK?

38:37.182 --> 38:40.185
- THAT'S GOING ON
ALL DAY, EVERY DAY.

38:40.185 --> 38:42.054
MY SON IS SUFFERING.

38:42.054 --> 38:43.822
HAVE YOU NO SOUL?

38:43.822 --> 38:45.724
- IF YOU FILL OUT
AN APPLICATION NOW,

38:45.724 --> 38:47.659
I CAN ALMOST GUARANTEE
THAT FOR NEXT YEAR--

38:47.659 --> 38:50.996
- HE DOESN'T HAVE A YEAR!

38:50.996 --> 38:53.231
- [whimpers]

38:53.231 --> 38:54.900
THERE'S A CAMP.

38:54.900 --> 38:58.904
ALL THE SPOTS ARE FULL,
BUT THERE'S A QUADRIPLEGIC.

38:58.904 --> 39:00.305
HE WON'T GET MUCH
OUT OF IT.

39:00.305 --> 39:02.441
I CAN BUMP HIM FOR CARL.

39:02.441 --> 39:03.408
- CAMP?

39:03.408 --> 39:04.710
- LIKE SUMMER CAMP?

39:04.710 --> 39:06.645
- IT'S BEAUTIFUL,
ON A LAKE--

39:06.645 --> 39:10.248
A WONDERFUL PLACE
FOR CHILDREN TO FEEL NORMAL

39:10.248 --> 39:12.084
ONE LAST TIME.

39:12.084 --> 39:14.386
- WHAT THE HELL AM I SUPPOSED TO
DO WITH A TRIP TO CANCER CAMP?

39:14.386 --> 39:16.521
- I'VE NEVER BEEN TO CAMP.

39:16.521 --> 39:19.424
[baby crying]

39:19.424 --> 39:24.663
- JIMMY, COME SIT WITH ME.
I WANT TO SHOW YOU SOMETHING.

39:27.933 --> 39:29.501
COME!

39:34.940 --> 39:36.575
- HEY.

39:36.575 --> 39:40.812
- ALL OF THIS
ROMANTIC PRETENDING, AMOR,

39:40.812 --> 39:44.549
IT MAKE ME SO HOT...

39:44.549 --> 39:48.286
AND WET.

39:48.286 --> 39:49.788
- OW.

39:49.788 --> 39:51.590
- FEEL.
- OW.

39:51.590 --> 39:54.059
- WE SHOULD NOT PUT
ALL THAT WATER TO WASTE, NO?

39:54.059 --> 39:56.795
- NO?
- NO.

39:56.795 --> 39:57.829
- OW.
- NO.

39:57.829 --> 39:59.131
- ESTE, ESTE, LISTEN.

39:59.131 --> 40:00.665
I-I--
- YES?

40:00.665 --> 40:04.136
- I-I CAN'T.
- YES.

40:04.136 --> 40:06.938
I-I--
- YES!

40:06.938 --> 40:08.673
- I CAN'T.
- YES!

40:08.673 --> 40:10.976
- NO.
I CAN'T!

40:10.976 --> 40:12.844
- [moans]

40:12.844 --> 40:15.614
- I--NO, I CAN'T.
- YES!

40:15.614 --> 40:18.683
- OH, FUCK!
- YES! [moans]

40:29.961 --> 40:32.631
[indistinct conversation]

40:43.708 --> 40:45.577
- ALL RIGHT,
WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO?

40:45.577 --> 40:48.680
WHOSE ASS AM I KICKING FIRST?
- THERE'S NO ASS TO KICK.

40:48.680 --> 40:51.750
KEV'S A LITTLE BOY WITH
A "WHITE PICKET FENCE" FANTASY,

40:51.750 --> 40:54.219
AND IN WALKS HIS WIFE
WITH HIS SON.

40:54.219 --> 40:55.620
- WE DON'T KNOW
THAT'S HIS KID.

40:55.620 --> 40:57.689
SO FIRST THING WE DO
IS GET A PATERNITY TEST.

40:57.689 --> 40:59.191
- IT'S NOT ABOUT BLOOD
TO KEV.

40:59.191 --> 41:01.393
THERE'S A WOMAN
HE GREW UP WITH AND MARRIED

41:01.393 --> 41:03.562
SAYING HER SON IS HIS.

41:03.562 --> 41:06.198
- THAT'S STUPID.
- IT'S NOT. LOOK AT YOU.

41:06.198 --> 41:07.899
YOU'RE A MOTHER
TO YOUR KIDS.

41:07.899 --> 41:10.135
DOESN'T MATTER
YOU DIDN'T PUSH THEM OUT.

41:13.605 --> 41:16.374
KEV'S THE FIRST GOOD MAN
I'VE EVER LOVED, YOU KNOW?

41:16.374 --> 41:19.845
MY FIRST LOVE WAS
NAMED APOLLO, ENOUGH SAID.

41:19.845 --> 41:21.379
THEN THERE WAS SPIDER.

41:21.379 --> 41:22.714
- [laughs]
SPIDER?

41:22.714 --> 41:24.449
- YOU CAN'T MAKE
THAT SHIT UP.

41:27.552 --> 41:28.954
NO, I...

41:28.954 --> 41:31.857
I CAN'T FIGHT FOR KEV.

41:31.857 --> 41:33.692
ASKING HIM TO PICK ME
OVER THEM

41:33.692 --> 41:36.294
IS ASKING HIM TO CHANGE
THE THING ABOUT HIM

41:36.294 --> 41:39.397
THAT I LOVE THE MOST.

41:39.397 --> 41:40.866
- SCREW THAT.

41:40.866 --> 41:42.467
- FI...
- NO.

41:42.467 --> 41:45.637
SCREW THAT.
- FIONA.

41:45.637 --> 41:49.441
SIT--FI!

41:49.441 --> 41:52.944
- GOOD CATCH.
- KEV!

41:52.944 --> 41:55.347
WHAT THE FUCK?
- THERE'S KIDS AROUND.

41:55.347 --> 41:57.349
- OH, YOU THINK
THEY HAVEN'T HEARD IT BEFORE?

41:57.349 --> 41:59.918
WHAT, ARE YOU DRUNK?
- NO, I'M NOT DRUNK.

41:59.918 --> 42:01.453
I'M OUT OF MY MIND,
'CAUSE YOU AND V

42:01.453 --> 42:03.188
ARE THE ONLY THINGS
THAT HAVE EVER MADE SENSE

42:03.188 --> 42:04.756
TO ME IN THIS
WHOLE FUCKED UP WORLD.

42:04.756 --> 42:06.258
OKAY, IF YOU GUYS
CAN'T MAKE IT,

42:06.258 --> 42:08.627
JIMMY AND I SHOULD
JUST QUIT RIGHT NOW.

42:08.627 --> 42:11.363
I SWEAR TO GOD,
IF YOU LEAVE V--

42:11.363 --> 42:13.231
- WHO'S LEAVING V?
- YOU'RE LEAVING V?

42:13.231 --> 42:14.900
- NO.
FIONA, WHAT THE HELL?

42:14.900 --> 42:17.302
- THE NOTARY, KEV,
THE DIVORCE PAPERS?

42:17.302 --> 42:18.637
- OH!

42:18.637 --> 42:20.672
SHIT. I HAD SOME DRINKS.

42:20.672 --> 42:23.475
AND CHERYL
DROPPED THIS KID BOMB, AND--

42:23.475 --> 42:25.677
AND I FORGOT.
- HEY!

42:25.677 --> 42:27.646
YOU'RE INTERRUPTING.
- EXCUSE ME?

42:27.646 --> 42:31.116
- KEV'S TRYING
TO GET TO KNOW HIS SON.

42:31.116 --> 42:35.120
GIVE MY BOYS THEIR TIME.

42:35.120 --> 42:37.355
- YOUR BOYS?
- FIONA, FIONA.

42:37.355 --> 42:38.857
IT'S NOT--
IT'S NOT WHAT YOU THINK.

42:38.857 --> 42:41.760
LOOK, CHERYL AND I
HAVE HISTORY--THAT'S IT.

42:41.760 --> 42:43.628
AND SHE'S NOT TRYING
TO STEAL ME AWAY FROM V.

42:43.628 --> 42:46.431
SHE JUST WANTS ME
TO MEET MY SON.

42:49.267 --> 42:53.038
- I KNOW SCHOOL
WAS NEVER YOUR THING,

42:53.038 --> 42:54.506
BUT YOU'VE NEVER
BEEN DUMB.

42:54.506 --> 42:56.708
IF YOU DON'T SEE
WHAT HAPPENING HERE,

42:56.708 --> 42:59.077
JUST PLAIN DUMB.

42:59.077 --> 43:01.313
COME ON, DEBS, DINNERTIME.

43:01.313 --> 43:04.249
- CAN KYLE COME?
- NO.

43:06.851 --> 43:08.186
- ALL RIGHT.

43:08.186 --> 43:09.654
- YOU KNOW, MY MOTHER,

43:09.654 --> 43:11.856
SHE REMINDS ME VERY MUCH
OF YOUR FIONA--

43:11.856 --> 43:16.628
BEAUTIFUL, RAISED SIX KIDS,
NEVER COMPLAINED, A SAINT.

43:16.628 --> 43:20.031
MY FATHER, HE WAS A...

43:20.031 --> 43:21.700
[speaking Portuguese]

43:21.700 --> 43:24.836
A ROLLING STONE.
- SHE PUT MY HAND THERE.

43:24.836 --> 43:28.139
I DIDN'T EVEN MOVE IT.

43:28.139 --> 43:32.077
- THAT IS SOMETHING EXACTLY
LIKE MY FATHER WOULD HAVE SAID.

43:37.248 --> 43:38.817
- DID THAT FATTY
ACTUALLY COP A FEEL?

43:38.817 --> 43:40.352
- HE TOTALLY COPPED A FEEL.

43:40.352 --> 43:42.387
[laughs]
- YOU GOT TO BE KIDDING ME.

43:42.387 --> 43:44.823
I MEAN,
WHAT'S UP WITH THAT?

43:44.823 --> 43:47.926
- SHIT, MICKEY.
WHAT THE HELL YOU DOING HERE?

43:47.926 --> 43:49.828
- AH, FROM THE STORE, RIGHT?

43:49.828 --> 43:52.063
OH, COME ON, IAN,
DON'T BE RUDE.

43:52.063 --> 43:53.698
INVITE YOUR BOYFRIEND
BACK TO MY PLACE.

43:53.698 --> 43:55.400
I MEAN, THE MORE
THE MERRIER, RIGHT?

43:55.400 --> 43:57.435
[chuckles]
- I'M SORRY.

43:57.435 --> 44:00.305
WHAT'D YOU CALL ME?
- WHAT?

44:00.305 --> 44:01.740
- OH, JESUS, MICKEY!

44:01.740 --> 44:03.041
- FAGGOT.

44:03.041 --> 44:04.509
WHAT THE FUCK
DID YOU CALL ME, FAGGOT?

44:04.509 --> 44:06.711
- ENOUGH. ENOUGH!

44:06.711 --> 44:09.314
[horn honking]

44:11.416 --> 44:12.717
- WHAT THE FUCK, GALLAGHER?
- SHIT, MICKEY.

44:12.717 --> 44:15.053
THEY'RE GONNA CALL THE COPS.

44:15.053 --> 44:17.589
ARE YOU OKAY?
- COME ON!

44:17.589 --> 44:19.491
- SORRY.
- GALLAGHER!

44:19.491 --> 44:23.828
- SORRY.
I'LL TEXT YOU.

44:23.828 --> 44:25.363
AH, SHIT!

44:34.739 --> 44:37.075
WHAT THE FUCK
IS WRONG WITH YOU?

44:37.075 --> 44:40.278
- [laughs]

44:40.278 --> 44:43.915
[both laughing]

44:49.220 --> 44:51.489
- WHERE'D YOU LEARN THIS?

44:51.489 --> 44:54.426
- NOWHERE.
JUST RELAX AND ENJOY.

44:54.426 --> 44:56.094
- YOU BEEN WATCHING PORN
WITHOUT ME?

44:56.094 --> 44:57.729
'CAUSE, YOU KNOW,
I CONSIDER THAT CHEATING.

44:57.729 --> 44:59.397
- NO, I HAVEN'T,

44:59.397 --> 45:01.399
ALTHOUGH I DO CONSIDER
THAT RULE PRETTY UNREALISTIC.

45:01.399 --> 45:04.202
I JUST THOUGHT IT UP.

45:04.202 --> 45:06.604
IT'S HOT, RIGHT?

45:06.604 --> 45:09.374
- MAYBE IF I WAS LICKING IT
OFF YOU.

45:09.374 --> 45:11.910
I'M HUNGRY.
TRADE PLACES.

45:11.910 --> 45:14.279
- NO.
- NO?

45:14.279 --> 45:18.583
[chuckles] SINCE WHEN
DO YOU TURN DOWN A B.J.?

45:18.583 --> 45:21.586
YOUR DICK'S
NOT EVEN HARD.

45:28.626 --> 45:31.629
- WHAT?
I DID A LITTLE MANSCAPING.

45:33.798 --> 45:35.667
SHIT.

45:35.667 --> 45:37.402
IT'S NOT MY FAULT, OKAY?

45:37.402 --> 45:40.205
WHAT--SHE'S A PEDOPHILE!

45:40.205 --> 45:43.208
LOOK, IT WAS
A STING OPERATION.

45:43.208 --> 45:45.143
LOOK, I TOOK A PICTURE
FOR THE COPS.

45:45.143 --> 45:49.180
- FUCK THE COPS.
THEY HAD THEIR CHANCE.

45:49.180 --> 45:50.949
- SHIT.

45:56.121 --> 45:58.990
[sighs]

46:00.391 --> 46:02.327
SMELLS GOOD.
- WHAT'S WITH MANDY?

46:02.327 --> 46:04.329
- AH, SOMETHING
SHE WANTED TO DO.

46:04.329 --> 46:06.965
WHERE'S JIMMY?
- NO IDEA.

46:06.965 --> 46:09.000
- WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR HEAD, CARL?

46:09.000 --> 46:10.468
- LICE.
- AGAIN?

46:10.468 --> 46:11.936
- YEAH, FRANK SHAVED IT.

46:11.936 --> 46:14.038
- YEAH, AND HE GOT ME
INTO A SUMMER CAMP.

46:14.038 --> 46:15.607
- WHAT?
WHY WOULD HE DO THAT?

46:15.607 --> 46:17.208
- I DON'T KNOW.
BUT IT'S COOL, RIGHT?

46:17.208 --> 46:19.444
- YEAH, IT'S AWESOME, CARL.

46:22.814 --> 46:25.650
[sighs]

46:31.456 --> 46:34.159
[door closes]

46:39.497 --> 46:43.568
- I'M GONNA KNOW MY KID.

46:43.568 --> 46:45.236
I'M GONNA KNOW MY KID,

46:45.236 --> 46:49.741
AND YOU CAN'T HAVE
A PROBLEM WITH THAT.

46:49.741 --> 46:52.510
LOOK, I...

46:52.510 --> 46:55.013
I DON'T CARE
ABOUT CHERYL, V.

46:55.013 --> 46:59.250
I USED TO, BUT SHE'S NOTHING
BUT A MEMORY TO ME NOW.

46:59.250 --> 47:01.286
AND I'M SORRY...

47:01.286 --> 47:05.023
[sighs]
I DIDN'T GO SEE THE NOTARY.

47:05.023 --> 47:09.661
BUT I WOULD
NEVER LEAVE YOU, EVER.

47:09.661 --> 47:12.564
YOU GOT TO KNOW THAT.

47:15.033 --> 47:19.904
AFTER EVERYTHING
WE'VE BEEN THROUGH,

47:19.904 --> 47:23.741
YOU KIND OF JUST HAVE
TO KNOW THAT.

47:26.711 --> 47:31.049
- [sobs]

47:31.049 --> 47:33.952
- WHOA. YOU JUST SNOTTED
THE WHOLE TABLE.

47:33.952 --> 47:35.787
[laughter]

47:35.787 --> 47:38.022
- KEV?

47:38.022 --> 47:39.090
KEV.

47:39.090 --> 47:43.695
[laughter]

47:43.695 --> 47:45.029
WHAT?
WHAT THE FUCK?

47:45.029 --> 47:47.065
ARE THEY LAUGHING AT ME?

47:47.065 --> 47:49.100
- NO.
- YES.

47:49.100 --> 47:50.435
- FIONA!
- FUCK YOU!

47:50.435 --> 47:52.470
- EXCUSE YOU?
- CHERYL, LISTEN--

47:52.470 --> 47:55.273
- NO, I'M DONE LISTENING.
KYLE, GO PACK OUR SHIT, NOW.

47:55.273 --> 47:57.075
- CHERYL, WOULD YOU JUST
LISTEN TO ME?

47:57.075 --> 47:58.743
- YOU COULD'VE HAD THIS,
AND YOU WANT THAT?

47:58.743 --> 48:00.345
SHE'S SOME KIND OF NYMPHO,

48:00.345 --> 48:01.813
HAS THREE DRAWERS
FULL OF DILDOS.

48:01.813 --> 48:03.615
- WHAT YOU DOING GOING THROUGH
MY SHIT, BITCH?

48:03.615 --> 48:04.882
- WHAT'S A DILDO?

48:04.882 --> 48:06.451
- CHERYL,
WOULD YOU JUST LISTEN?

48:06.451 --> 48:07.852
- YOU'RE JUST AS THICK
AS THE DAY I MET YOU.

48:07.852 --> 48:09.087
- CHERYL,
I GET THAT YOU'RE MAD,

48:09.087 --> 48:10.788
BUT I WANT TO BE
A FATHER TO KYLE.

48:10.788 --> 48:12.757
NOW, I'M GONNA GET YOU
A PLACE NEARBY.

48:12.757 --> 48:14.859
- HE'S NOT YOURS, KEV.
HE ISN'T EVEN MINE.

48:14.859 --> 48:18.396
HE'S MY SISTER'S,
YOU STUPID PIECE OF SHIT!

48:21.065 --> 48:23.101
- WHAT DID SHE SAY?

48:23.101 --> 48:24.402
WHAT DID SHE SAY?

48:24.402 --> 48:26.571
- WHAT THE FUCK, BITCH?
- GET HER, V!

48:26.571 --> 48:28.673
- I'LL FUCK YOU UP!
- GET HER!

48:28.673 --> 48:30.642
- [screams]
STOP HER!

48:30.642 --> 48:31.909
- WELL, SHOULD WE
STOP 'EM, OR--?

48:31.909 --> 48:33.511
- WHAT, YOU WANT TO
LOSE AN EYE?

48:33.511 --> 48:35.613
- AAH!
- YOU'RE A CRAZY BITCH!

48:35.613 --> 48:37.515
- KILL HER, V!
- AAH!

48:37.515 --> 48:40.418
- BITCH,
YOU COME INTO MY HOUSE

48:40.418 --> 48:41.786
AND MAKE UP
SOME SHIT LIKE THAT?

48:41.786 --> 48:44.088
- GET YOUR HANDS OFF ME,
YOU DIRTY BITCH!

48:44.088 --> 48:48.593
[screams]
GET HER OFF ME!

48:48.593 --> 48:51.596
- SHIT, THE TV!
- NO!

48:51.596 --> 48:54.365
NOT THE TV!

48:54.365 --> 48:56.100
- GET THE DIVORCE PAPERS, KEV.

48:56.100 --> 48:58.670
THIS BITCH IS ABOUT TO SIGN.
- I AIN'T SIGNING SHIT!

48:58.670 --> 49:02.407
- THIS WAY, THIS WAY.
- [screams]

49:02.407 --> 49:03.708
- IF YOU WANT TO WALK AWAY
WITH FOUR LIMBS, BITCH,

49:03.708 --> 49:05.777
YOU'RE GONNA SIGN.
KEV, THE PAPERS!

49:05.777 --> 49:07.412
- FUCK YOU!
- YOU'RE SIGNING!

49:07.412 --> 49:08.746
[snap]
- AAH!

49:08.746 --> 49:11.916
- SIGN THE PAPERS.
- AAH!

49:11.916 --> 49:13.685
- MM-HMM. MM-HMM.

49:13.685 --> 49:14.919
- [screams]

49:14.919 --> 49:16.654
- SIGN IT!

49:16.654 --> 49:18.690
- YOU COULD INITIAL THAT.

49:18.690 --> 49:22.160
- [grunts, panting]

49:26.664 --> 49:29.033
- UH-UH, NOT ONE WORD.
JUST DRIVE AWAY.

49:32.704 --> 49:34.639
[tires squeal]

49:34.639 --> 49:35.807
- WHOO.

49:35.807 --> 49:38.042
- BITCH, YOU SO CRAZY.

49:38.042 --> 49:39.844
- HELL, YEAH!

49:39.844 --> 49:43.481
[all cheering]

49:43.481 --> 49:45.650
HELL, YEAH!

49:48.986 --> 49:50.755
- YOU'RE STILL HERE.

49:50.755 --> 49:53.358
- YOU THINK I'M GETTING IN A CAR
WITH THAT PSYCHO?

49:53.358 --> 49:55.360
HEY, UH,
CAN I BORROW YOUR PHONE?

49:55.360 --> 49:57.729
I NEED TO CALL MY MOM--
MY OTHER MOM.

49:57.729 --> 50:00.865
- SURE.

50:00.865 --> 50:02.834
- YOU WANT TO EAT DINNER FIRST?

50:02.834 --> 50:06.237
- SURE.
- COOL.

50:09.640 --> 50:12.276
[knock at door]

50:18.216 --> 50:20.818
- YOU BLAKE?
- [shakily] YES.

50:20.818 --> 50:22.754
- YOU'RE MOVING NOW, BLAKE.

50:22.754 --> 50:25.390
YOU'RE MOVING TONIGHT.
- EXCUSE ME?

50:25.390 --> 50:28.593
- I DON'T EXCUSE YOU,
YOU SICK BITCH.

50:28.593 --> 50:30.962
I DON'T EXCUSE YOU
'CAUSE YOU'RE HOT

50:30.962 --> 50:32.397
OR 'CAUSE YOU'RE BLONDE
OR 'CAUSE

50:32.397 --> 50:33.931
OF WHAT YOU'VE GOT
BETWEEN YOUR LEGS.

50:33.931 --> 50:36.334
COME TAKE A LOOK.

50:38.970 --> 50:40.638
YOU SEE THAT?

50:40.638 --> 50:42.707
THEY'RE DIGGING
YOUR GRAVE.

50:42.707 --> 50:45.643
AND YOU WANT TO BE GONE BEFORE
THEY GET DOWN TO SIX FEET.

50:45.643 --> 50:47.645
HOW'S IT GOING, BOYS?
- GOOD.

50:47.645 --> 50:50.281
WE DUG THE BERLANTI GRAVE
IN WHAT, TWO HOURS?

50:50.281 --> 50:51.883
BUT THIS DIRT
IS NICE AND SOFT--

50:51.883 --> 50:54.886
GOING A LOT FASTER.
- TICKTOCK.

50:54.886 --> 50:59.190
- KID FUCKER.

50:59.190 --> 51:01.459
- [sighs deeply]

51:01.459 --> 51:05.730
- HEY.
- HEY.

51:05.730 --> 51:08.099
- YOU LOOKED STRESSED.

51:08.099 --> 51:09.233
- I DO?

51:09.233 --> 51:11.402
- HOW WAS YOUR DAY?
- GOOD.

51:11.402 --> 51:13.771
- HOW'D IT GO AT THE DOCTOR?

51:13.771 --> 51:18.176
- GOOD.
IT'S HEALING.

51:30.455 --> 51:33.658
HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY.

51:33.658 --> 51:38.029
- [crying]

51:38.029 --> 51:40.198
THE WORLD'S MESSED UP.

51:40.198 --> 51:42.700
SO MUCH UGLY SHIT HAPPENS.

51:42.700 --> 51:46.471
